snippet.title: Free Britney Spears| Johnny Depp Vs Amber Heard, Fast 9 Review & More
snippet.description:
We start off with Fast 9 & all the ridiculous action/twists Included. We talk spoilers, incl. the return of Han & what this means for the future of the franchise! We've done a month's worth of shows! Thank God Austin is back! What happened to him? Well... long story but luckily the cameras were rolling! PLUS! FREE BRITNEY! As Jack is the oldest member of the team he remembers when a 17 year old Britney Spears stormed the world! she is in an incredibly horrible situation and we discuss what led to it and how she can get justice! There's a Snyderverse box set coming out! Is this a good sign? I mean it seems Warner wants nothing to do with Snyder and the Snydercut; yet, a boxed trilogy is coming out! Hmm what could all this mean? Plus, Hollywood is moving full steam ahead as John Wick 4, Knives Out 2, & Aquaman 2 go into production! Again, fans are saturating social media once again with calls to get rid of Amber Heard! Remember the trial we did? We told you this wasn't going away. And we're talking about it! 1st openly gay player in the NFL has the world talking! Why hasn't this happened yet? Are people that afraid of openly gay athletes?  We're not! 

Plus more! So join us in the comments!
